00:02:23.256 --> 00:02:25.516
where Moshe got so fed up with them

00:02:25.556 --> 00:02:27.597
that just three days out of Choreb,

00:02:27.657 --> 00:02:28.758
he said, God,

00:02:28.798 --> 00:02:28.978
you've

00:02:29.585 --> 00:02:30.686
you might as well just kill me.

00:02:30.725 --> 00:02:31.907
No one can do this job.

00:02:31.948 --> 00:02:33.889
If you have any respect for me at

00:02:33.949 --> 00:02:34.150
all,

00:02:34.189 --> 00:02:37.354
you'll not have me continue to do this.

00:02:37.373 --> 00:02:38.735
This job cannot be done.

00:02:39.977 --> 00:02:44.701
And Dowd managed to hang in there longer

00:02:44.801 --> 00:02:45.242
even than

00:02:46.475 --> 00:02:47.217
Then Moshe did.

00:02:47.537 --> 00:02:49.598
Moshe was three days out of Choreb,

00:02:49.657 --> 00:02:51.280
although he did finish the job over the

00:02:51.819 --> 00:02:52.781
over forty years.

00:02:53.580 --> 00:02:54.382
To some extent,

00:02:54.401 --> 00:02:55.423
he mailed some of it in.

00:02:56.463 --> 00:02:59.045
But and he just got them to the

00:02:59.086 --> 00:03:00.887
promised land and not into it.

00:03:01.987 --> 00:03:03.588
As it relates to Dowd, he had.

00:03:04.729 --> 00:03:07.450
Really, forty-eight pretty good years.

00:03:07.790 --> 00:03:09.170
He started at eight years old,

00:03:09.230 --> 00:03:12.951
and it was fifty-six before he had his

00:03:13.012 --> 00:03:15.353
complete crash and burn.

00:03:16.973 --> 00:03:20.133
And what we read after his fiasco with

00:03:22.014 --> 00:03:26.675
Bathsheba and the elimination of the Light

00:03:26.935 --> 00:03:27.455
of Yah,

00:03:27.656 --> 00:03:29.795
which is the man that he had killed,

00:03:30.735 --> 00:03:32.937
her husband, Uriah,

00:03:34.092 --> 00:03:39.177
that Dowd became angry that God was

00:03:39.337 --> 00:03:40.758
judgmental of him,

00:03:41.278 --> 00:03:41.680
that God

00:03:43.048 --> 00:03:45.930
disassociated to a large extent.

00:03:45.949 --> 00:03:47.751
They were not on speaking terms.

00:03:48.570 --> 00:03:50.572
And rather than accept that he had been

00:03:50.592 --> 00:03:51.932
wrong and learn from it,

00:03:52.252 --> 00:03:53.213
we all make mistakes.

00:03:53.274 --> 00:03:54.914
We all are wrong at times.

00:03:55.155 --> 00:03:56.235
We all stumble and fall.

00:03:56.254 --> 00:03:58.256
And rather than Dowd getting back up and

00:03:58.937 --> 00:04:01.677
recognizing that he could learn from this

00:04:01.737 --> 00:04:04.099
experience and grow from it, Dowd didn't.

00:04:04.419 --> 00:04:05.980
He lashed out at God.

00:04:06.341 --> 00:04:11.463
And we had to go through the horrible

00:04:11.484 --> 00:04:12.104
experience

00:04:12.414 --> 00:04:16.295
that Dowd had toward Yahowah in the

00:04:16.315 --> 00:04:18.976
immediate aftermath of his blunder,

00:04:19.396 --> 00:04:21.298
which is recorded in the fifty-first

00:04:22.699 --> 00:04:24.079
Mashal, not Mashal,

00:04:24.098 --> 00:04:25.980
but of Mizmowr or Psalm.

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:27.459
And it's horrendous.

00:04:28.420 --> 00:04:30.000
And we dealt with it.

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:32.922
We didn't want to, but nonetheless,

00:04:33.002 --> 00:04:34.862
it's an important story to tell.

00:04:35.423 --> 00:04:38.863
And it is Dowd's feelings in this regard

00:04:39.324 --> 00:04:40.464
that really set up

00:04:41.521 --> 00:04:43.423
both Judaism and Christianity.

00:04:43.483 --> 00:04:44.625
Had he not done so,

00:04:45.446 --> 00:04:48.288
it would have been impossible for anyone

00:04:48.329 --> 00:04:52.233
to steal Dowd's title as the Messiah and

00:04:52.473 --> 00:04:54.975
son of God, as our savior,

00:04:55.557 --> 00:04:56.858
as the returning king.

00:04:57.559 --> 00:04:59.841
And to give it to, well,

00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:02.819
You know, in Christianity,

00:05:02.839 --> 00:05:04.420
it was stolen and given to the mythical

00:05:04.461 --> 00:05:04.961
Jesus.

00:05:05.581 --> 00:05:08.060
And in Judaism,

00:05:08.120 --> 00:05:10.982
it was stolen and given to the warlord

00:05:11.081 --> 00:05:11.822
Bar Kokhba.

00:05:12.982 --> 00:05:14.182
And that would never have happened,

00:05:14.281 --> 00:05:15.163
could not have happened,

00:05:15.622 --> 00:05:18.822
had Dowd not fallen so precipitously and

00:05:18.843 --> 00:05:22.684
then wallowed in his own shame.

00:05:22.744 --> 00:05:26.165
And what we learned is that a number

00:05:26.185 --> 00:05:26.504
of things.

00:05:26.545 --> 00:05:27.004
First of all,

00:05:29.975 --> 00:05:34.178
It was assumed but not stated that Dowd

00:05:34.798 --> 00:05:38.321
could not have served as the Passover

00:05:38.401 --> 00:05:38.802
lamb,

00:05:38.901 --> 00:05:40.302
even though they don't have their

00:05:40.382 --> 00:05:41.923
Jesus-fulfilling Passover,

00:05:42.904 --> 00:05:44.326
because he was not perfect,

00:05:45.165 --> 00:05:47.507
particularly because of the horrible

00:05:47.608 --> 00:05:50.790
failures associated with the Bathsheba

00:05:51.050 --> 00:05:51.350
affair.

00:05:52.937 --> 00:05:54.478
But one of the things that we have

00:05:54.579 --> 00:05:54.918
learned,

00:05:54.999 --> 00:05:57.678
and it's exceedingly important if you're

00:05:57.699 --> 00:05:59.060
going to have a relationship with God,

00:05:59.779 --> 00:06:01.339
is that he's not looking for perfect.

00:06:02.040 --> 00:06:04.040
He knows that there's no such thing as

00:06:04.120 --> 00:06:04.461
perfect.

00:06:04.841 --> 00:06:06.302
There's never been a perfect animal.

00:06:07.122 --> 00:06:10.043
Even his actions over the past have been

00:06:10.223 --> 00:06:11.283
imperfect at times.

00:06:12.103 --> 00:06:14.863
And that the reason God does not want

00:06:14.884 --> 00:06:17.684
and not looking for perfect is first,

00:06:17.803 --> 00:06:18.644
it's impossible.

00:06:19.404 --> 00:06:22.605
And second, it is undesirable.

00:06:23.125 --> 00:06:25.485
If we were perfect,

00:06:25.586 --> 00:06:28.026
we would be indistinguishable.

00:06:28.526 --> 00:06:29.826
We would be boring.

00:06:29.867 --> 00:06:32.168
We'd have no character.

00:06:32.228 --> 00:06:35.528
We'd have no ability to learn.

00:06:35.569 --> 00:06:38.309
We'd have nothing that we could offer.

00:06:38.329 --> 00:06:40.170
We'd have no way of proving our worth.

00:06:41.199 --> 00:06:42.142
We could not grow.

00:06:43.213 --> 00:06:45.636
And so it would be actually

00:06:45.675 --> 00:06:47.096
counterproductive to be perfect.

00:06:47.617 --> 00:06:48.517
God's not looking for that.

00:06:48.557 --> 00:06:50.579
He is looking for, are you observant?

00:06:50.819 --> 00:06:51.180
In other words,

00:06:51.199 --> 00:06:52.661
do you closely examine and carefully

00:06:52.721 --> 00:06:56.622
consider what he has to say and what

00:06:57.144 --> 00:07:00.586
appears all around us so that ultimately

00:07:00.605 --> 00:07:02.466
you would be a good travel companion going

00:07:02.507 --> 00:07:04.928
through the universe with God.

00:07:05.028 --> 00:07:06.529
Second of all, are you responsive?

00:07:06.589 --> 00:07:08.250
Are you willing to engage?

00:07:08.271 --> 00:07:10.452
Are you willing to make a relationship

00:07:10.473 --> 00:07:10.892
with God?

00:07:10.992 --> 00:07:16.276
You're not someone who is expecting

00:07:16.336 --> 00:07:17.136
entitlements.

00:07:17.476 --> 00:07:19.497
You don't expect God to do everything and

00:07:19.517 --> 00:07:21.459
you have to do nothing like the nature

00:07:21.519 --> 00:07:21.579
of...

00:07:22.192 --> 00:07:25.093
Christianity, or in the case of Judaism,

00:07:25.113 --> 00:07:26.014
it's just the opposite.

00:07:26.093 --> 00:07:27.915
People do everything and God does nothing.

00:07:28.634 --> 00:07:30.435
But in these opposites,

00:07:31.115 --> 00:07:32.555
you're not either of those two.

00:07:32.636 --> 00:07:34.235
You're willing to listen to God,

00:07:34.795 --> 00:07:36.137
pay attention to what he has to say,

00:07:36.177 --> 00:07:36.976
and then respond,

00:07:37.757 --> 00:07:39.377
contributing to the relationship,

00:07:39.418 --> 00:07:42.259
making everything better by your response.

00:07:42.319 --> 00:07:44.978
And number four is the most interesting of

00:07:45.059 --> 00:07:45.259
all.

00:07:45.759 --> 00:07:49.160
God wants us to demonstrate that we are

00:07:49.500 --> 00:07:50.161
reliable,

00:07:50.321 --> 00:07:50.761
that we

00:07:51.240 --> 00:07:54.081
can be trusted he wants to remove us

00:07:54.483 --> 00:07:56.483
from these physical bodies from the

00:07:56.524 --> 00:07:58.785
restraints of these bodies so that we can

00:07:58.805 --> 00:08:00.324
go off and explore the universe with him

00:08:00.725 --> 00:08:04.266
so that we can enter the seventh dimension

00:08:04.387 --> 00:08:07.269
and be with him so that the gap

00:08:07.288 --> 00:08:09.370
between who we are and who he is

00:08:09.470 --> 00:08:12.350
is narrowed with uh us being raised up

00:08:12.391 --> 00:08:13.872
to his level and

00:08:14.432 --> 00:08:16.776
He can't do that responsibly.

00:08:16.815 --> 00:08:19.540
He shouldn't do that until such time as

00:08:19.581 --> 00:08:21.584
we demonstrate that we can be trusted with

00:08:22.206 --> 00:08:24.269
all of that increased power and knowledge

00:08:24.310 --> 00:08:26.072
and capability.

00:08:26.192 --> 00:08:27.615
And so with Dowd,

00:08:28.172 --> 00:08:30.392
God came up with a very interesting way

00:08:31.173 --> 00:08:34.375
of resolving this dispute between the two

00:08:34.434 --> 00:08:34.735
of them,

00:08:34.815 --> 00:08:39.996
where Dowd had not just fallen and made

00:08:40.017 --> 00:08:40.957
a mess of things,

00:08:41.418 --> 00:08:42.778
but had lashed out at God,

00:08:42.817 --> 00:08:44.818
blaming God for this situation.

00:08:45.679 --> 00:08:48.221
Dowd became Yisrael.

00:08:48.721 --> 00:08:51.682
I became the same Yisrael that we

00:08:51.701 --> 00:08:53.283
witnessed during the Exodus,

00:08:53.702 --> 00:08:55.923
the same Yisrael that we witness today.

00:08:56.543 --> 00:08:57.465
He became Yisrael.

00:08:59.028 --> 00:09:03.168
belligerent and antagonistic towards God.

00:09:05.037 --> 00:09:07.337
And what Dowd demonstrates by the way that

00:09:07.378 --> 00:09:09.498
God resolved this problem is that it can

00:09:09.518 --> 00:09:10.138
be resolved.

00:09:10.177 --> 00:09:12.938
So there is hope for Yahuwdym and for

00:09:12.958 --> 00:09:15.840
Yisrael now because God resolved this

00:09:15.879 --> 00:09:18.379
problem with Dowd.

00:09:18.740 --> 00:09:21.280
And he did so in a most fascinating

00:09:21.341 --> 00:09:21.640
way.

00:09:21.701 --> 00:09:23.681
It's something that, again,

00:09:23.740 --> 00:09:27.241
we have just begun to explore because it

00:09:27.322 --> 00:09:30.363
is so fascinating.

00:09:30.700 --> 00:09:30.860
Well,

00:09:31.159 --> 00:09:32.721
it's the last thing you would actually

00:09:32.760 --> 00:09:34.561
expect, I suppose,

00:09:34.620 --> 00:09:37.461
even though it's been there all the time.

00:09:37.682 --> 00:09:38.522
You know,

00:09:38.562 --> 00:09:41.003
when you go back in time and you

00:09:41.043 --> 00:09:43.043
realize that Enoch,

00:09:43.182 --> 00:09:45.524
who was the first person,

00:09:45.583 --> 00:09:46.884
his name is actually Chanowk,

00:09:46.943 --> 00:09:50.144
it means that he is prepared and that

00:09:50.485 --> 00:09:53.125
then he is deployed by God,

00:09:53.145 --> 00:09:54.105
that's what his name means,

00:09:54.645 --> 00:09:54.785
that

00:09:55.365 --> 00:09:58.568
He uniquely appealed to Yahowah,

00:09:59.448 --> 00:10:01.971
found Yahowah, engaged in a relationship,

00:10:02.091 --> 00:10:04.493
demonstrated that he could meet those

00:10:04.533 --> 00:10:06.835
three criteria that God was looking for.

00:10:06.914 --> 00:10:09.797
Pay attention, respond, and be reliable.

00:10:09.876 --> 00:10:13.438
And God took him for that purpose so

00:10:13.479 --> 00:10:15.500
that he could redeploy him.

00:10:15.640 --> 00:10:16.761
And redeploy him he has.

00:10:17.866 --> 00:10:20.587
And by starting with someone that existed

00:10:20.628 --> 00:10:21.408
very early on,

00:10:21.467 --> 00:10:22.828
fifty-four hundred years ago,

00:10:24.089 --> 00:10:27.831
God was able to reinsert him,

00:10:28.971 --> 00:10:31.971
just taking his nephesh soul and Neshama,

00:10:32.912 --> 00:10:33.493
conscience,

00:10:34.052 --> 00:10:39.195
and reasserting that in a temporary Basar

00:10:39.235 --> 00:10:42.235
body, using DNA to reconstruct the body.

00:10:43.472 --> 00:10:43.993
Putting him in.

00:10:44.994 --> 00:10:47.755
And so long as God started with him

00:10:47.995 --> 00:10:49.777
early on, fifty four hundred years ago,

00:10:49.797 --> 00:10:50.758
it's pretty early on.

00:10:51.339 --> 00:10:55.000
And then I inserted him when need be

00:10:55.041 --> 00:10:58.082
to keep his people and plan on track.

00:10:58.783 --> 00:11:00.705
Then God could do so without interfering

00:11:00.725 --> 00:11:02.485
with free will and without making such a

00:11:02.546 --> 00:11:05.268
scene that he becomes undeniable.

00:11:05.749 --> 00:11:07.250
It's the best of all worlds.

00:11:07.289 --> 00:11:10.251
And God did that very thing.

00:11:11.655 --> 00:11:12.876
with his beloved son, Dowd.

00:11:13.738 --> 00:11:16.000
He walked away, as he must,

00:11:16.419 --> 00:11:19.182
when Dowd became so contentious and

00:11:19.221 --> 00:11:19.763
belligerent,

00:11:20.562 --> 00:11:22.124
and rather than giving up on him,

00:11:22.284 --> 00:11:23.525
which he could not do,

00:11:23.765 --> 00:11:24.826
and without

00:11:26.764 --> 00:11:28.585
ending the entire human experience.

00:11:28.605 --> 00:11:30.105
There would have been no purpose in

00:11:30.145 --> 00:11:32.647
creating mankind for creating this planet

00:11:32.726 --> 00:11:35.488
to conducive to life for the entire human

00:11:35.528 --> 00:11:36.129
experience,

00:11:36.149 --> 00:11:39.370
for even sharing the Towrah and creating

00:11:39.409 --> 00:11:43.072
the Mow'ed and the covenant, the Beryth.

00:11:44.013 --> 00:11:45.793
It's all for naught if God couldn't

00:11:45.854 --> 00:11:48.355
reestablish his relationship with Dowd.

00:11:48.434 --> 00:11:50.336
And yet he wasn't talking to him just

00:11:50.416 --> 00:11:52.076
as he's not talking to Israel.

00:11:52.966 --> 00:11:54.547
So something had to happen.

00:11:54.847 --> 00:11:57.648
God had to intervene in a way that

00:11:57.687 --> 00:12:00.149
he could communicate with Dowd,

00:12:00.188 --> 00:12:01.168
get his attention,

00:12:01.249 --> 00:12:03.350
get the relationship restored,

00:12:03.389 --> 00:12:06.431
and then ultimately Dowd's reputation

00:12:06.650 --> 00:12:09.572
